          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Serial Number (optional)" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Seriennummer (optional)"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Serial Number (required)" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Seriennummer (erforderlich)"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Setup" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Einrichtung"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Slicer Setup" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Slicer-Einrichtung"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Test Connection" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Verbindung testen"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This step is optional for using this app, but required to send prints over LAN." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Dieser Schritt ist optional für die App-Nutzung, aber nötig, um Drucke über LAN zu senden."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "To send prints over LAN, you'll also need to update your slicer's connection settings." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Um Drucke über LAN zu senden, musst du auch die Verbindungseinstellungen deines Slicers aktualisieren."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "View on Bambu Wiki" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Im Bambu Wiki ansehen"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Welcome to PandaBeFree" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Willkommen bei PandaBeFree"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "You can change notification preferences anytime in **More > Notifications**." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Du kannst die Benachrichtigungseinstellungen jederzeit unter **Mehr > Mitteilungen** ändern."
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "You'll need the following information from your printer:" : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Du benötigst die folgenden Informationen von deinem Drucker:"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Your iPhone must be on the same network as your printer (LAN mode only). Using a VPN like Tailscale or WireGuard is the easiest way to connect remotely." : {
      "localizations" : {
        "de" : {
          "stringUnit" : {
            "state" : "translated",
            "value" : "Dein iPhone muss im selben Netzwerk wie dein Drucker sein (nur LAN Mode). Ein VPN wie Tailscale oder WireGuard ist die einfachste Möglichkeit für den Fernzugriff."
          }
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "version" : "1.1"
}
